# ============================================================================
# ProductOS — Environment Variable Template
# ============================================================================
# Copy to .env.local:  cp .env.example .env.local
# Keys marked [REQUIRED] must be set for the app to boot.
# Keys marked [OPTIONAL] enable specific features but aren't needed for Day 1.
# ============================================================================

# === Supabase (Local Docker) [REQUIRED] ===
